                  try
                  {
                        $ErrorLogAccess = get_package( 'error_log::error_log_access' , 'last' , __FILE__ );
                        $ErrorLogAccess->add_message_to_log( 1 , 'title' , 'description' );
                        $Messages = $ErrorLogAccess->unsafe_select_messages( '1 ORDER BY id DESC LIMIT 0 , 1' );
                        
                        if( count( $Messages ) != 1 )
                        {
                              return( 'Illegal messages count' );
                        }
